  "3021630": {
    "name": "Savara",
    "steam_appid": 3021630,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/e27936fe493bb2c2efa1a5c10b5e8d0d.poster.avif?t=1771249028\" width=614 height=614 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/e27936fe493bb2c2efa1a5c10b5e8d0d.webm?t=1771249028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/e27936fe493bb2c2efa1a5c10b5e8d0d.mp4?t=1771249028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款精彩纷呈丰富多彩的Roguelite动作类游戏中，你将沉浸式探索一个令人迷人的世界，在这里，每个抉择都至关重要，每项策略都将得到回报，尽情探索这个迷人的世界吧！。你受邀参加为战神伊奥普举办的盛大庆典。此项庆祝活动非比寻常——它也是对这个世界最勇敢战士的一次考验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带上你最强的武器，精心挑选你的装备，准备好迎接巨大挑战。兵器各有千秋，此事关乎生死成败，须得谨慎挑选。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次胜利都将引领你走向更大的挑战，每一次失败都让你变得更强。利用在战斗中获得的资源来强化你的武器，在铁匠那里提升你的装备，并向神像供奉祭品以获得额外的庇佑。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场战斗庆典中，展现你的勇气和才能，追求无上属于你的荣耀。把握每场战斗机会，都是证明你值得赢得战神伊奥普的关注与祝福的机会。进入这个充满活力与危险的世界并取得胜利，成为这个独特维度中最伟大的战士吧。踏入这个充满活力、危机四伏的世界，战胜一切，成为最强战士，赢得至高荣耀！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>•\t最终试炼</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身扮演战神伊奥普最新的新晋勇士萨瓦拉，对抗史诗级生物，铸就属于你的传奇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/109559d23cf120c6cb2cdc94a093c052.poster.avif?t=1771249028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/109559d23cf120c6cb2cdc94a093c052.webm?t=1771249028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/109559d23cf120c6cb2cdc94a093c052.mp4?t=1771249028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>•\t预见为王</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为一名精锐战士，找出对手敌人的弱点，伺机而动，在最佳时机击败敌人，取得胜利。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>•\t 物尽其用</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败怪物，收集从击败的怪物身上掉落的材料，打造完美的武器库，整装待发，迎接新的挑战准备重新投入战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/66dd82949ddef265d0d24295b61795d6.poster.avif?t=1771249028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/66dd82949ddef265d0d24295b61795d6.webm?t=1771249028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/66dd82949ddef265d0d24295b61795d6.mp4?t=1771249028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>•\t武器选择</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是突刺还是斩击，一刀流是二刀流，共有四种风格、六种变体和数百种组合供君你选择——激发充分发挥你武器的最大潜力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>•\t战士休息一下？不没必了要！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >效忠于神灵，解锁90多种神赐圣祝福力量，自定义你的天赋与技能，提升你的装备，可玩性游戏体验拉满！在萨瓦拉，可以跌倒，但必须再站起来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/7bb3738bf661c4093dc92183147d331e.poster.avif?t=1771249028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/7bb3738bf661c4093dc92183147d331e.webm?t=1771249028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021630/extras/7bb3738bf661c4093dc92183147d331e.mp4?t=1771249028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入萨瓦拉，踏上史诗般的征程，迎接每一场战斗，都将引领你走向终极荣耀！</strong></p>",
